title: Finn Again
description: This is an alternate cover edition of ASIN B01DCM6FHY.Revisit the Finn Family as they prepare for Christmas Eve and the Curious Wedding of Owen Finn and Jeremy Porter. From bachelor parties with penis cakes to proposals and new revelations, the family has one heck of a holiday season. Are you Team Owen or Team Jeremy? Whatever side of the aisle you’re sitting on, you’ll finally get to see the wedding we’ve all been waiting for.  And maybe catch a glimpse of a few new members of the Finn Club…  *This is not a stand-alone as much as a revisiting of previous series characters, but it is the 5th story in the Finn Factor series.   Warning: This holiday feel good is full of nookie. m/m, m/m/f, m/m again…and some more m/m
author: R.G. Alexander
